summary:
As a communication advisor, I've always advocated for human rights and aimed to improve lives. First through working for various NGOs and the United Nations; now at the communication agency Tappan. I work on social projects and I'm involved with corporate social responsibility, and diversity&inclusion. 

I'm also a certified makeup artist. I do makeup at photoshoots, and I give (personal) makeup advice in one-on-one sessions and workshops.
